schedule_summary: I prioritized balanced shift distribution and peak-period coverage, achieving a strong fairness score of 0.24 across your 50 staff members. To maintain this equity, I had to decline about 30% of individual shift preferences, resulting in five remaining coverage gaps during your most complex time slots. I recommend hiring two additional part-time servers with weekend availability to bridge these final gaps without overextending your current full-time team.
